# Original full-resolution source photos (~182 MB). Kept out of git to keep the repo
# lean and to avoid deploying the originals. The site serves only the generated
# variants (assets/images/generated/), which ARE committed.
# >>> Keep your own backup of this folder — you need it to re-encode image variants.
# >>> Delete the line below if you prefer to version the originals in git.
01-website-ready-to-upload/assets/images/photos/
